WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:04.798
Hey, good morning family. Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining us today.

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:09.234
Well, it's Diana and Brandon today and we're so thankful that you all are watching us today.

00:00:09.235 --> 00:00:12.341
There's some things on my heart to talk about, but I didn't have a lot.

00:00:12.342 --> 00:00:22.129
But I told Diana, I said, "I feel in my spirit to make a video."I was out working in the yard, and there's a lot of things you all been discouraged about with the red heifers.

00:00:22.130 --> 00:00:31.422
They're saying at the Temple Institute that all the red heifers from Texas didn't qualify for the temple ceremony.

00:00:31.423 --> 00:00:38.323
And at first I was kind of like, "Man, that's a real bummer."I told Diana, I said, "Man, what does that mean, you know?

00:00:38.324 --> 00:00:59.919
Does that mean that delays the return of the Lord and all that?"But inside, I feel there's something afoot, you know, like I feel that there's something more to this because after she started studying it out, you know, I told her, she's like, "Oh no, Brandon, does that mean, you know?"And I said, "Hold on, let's just study and just what is it about the red heifer?

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:09.271
What is it about all this stuff? Because people are so disappointed about it."So after Diana was doing the research on it, you know, and finding out that they're very secretive.

00:01:09.272 --> 00:01:16.009
They don't talk about things because it's very controversial and they don't want rioting.

00:01:16.010 --> 00:01:22.600
They don't want an uprising of any kind of governmental, of anything, you know.

00:01:22.601 --> 00:01:27.606
So, it's holy for one, a very holy thing to the Jewish people.

00:01:27.607 --> 00:01:36.393
And looking for this red heifer without any kind of—it can't have more than two red, different color hairs on it.

00:01:36.394 --> 00:01:44.397
It's a perfect red heifer. And so, supposedly, out of these cows, they didn't all qualify.

00:01:44.398 --> 00:01:49.723
They disqualified. So this is like how many weeks before the Feast of Trumpets?

00:01:49.724 --> 00:01:57.356
We have like seven weeks now, and they just come out and say this this week. And I thought, but they had a practice run.

00:01:57.357 --> 00:02:05.593
So they had their practice run, and they saw what it would be like to do this event. Hasn't happened in 2,000 years.

00:02:05.594 --> 00:02:11.846
And then all of a sudden this week they come out and say, "Well, sorry folks, it's all messed up.

00:02:11.847 --> 00:02:16.392
Not all of them are bad. We're not going to be able to do it at all now. It's back to stage one.

00:02:16.393 --> 00:02:23.089
We have to go looking for one, and we've been looking for all this time."So, could that be true?

00:02:23.090 --> 00:02:30.165
Yes. But I feel in my spirit, I'm just, you know—I don't have a word from God concerning it. I don't.

00:02:30.166 --> 00:02:38.205
But inside of me, I'm thinking, could they be trying to, you know, like sleight of hand again? "Don't pay attention over here.

00:02:38.206 --> 00:02:44.303
Don't pay attention over here as we're doing something over here,"because they want to do it in September.

00:02:44.304 --> 00:02:50.799
I told you September is a very, very high alert month. This is the month. Here we go.

00:02:50.800 --> 00:03:00.442
We're just, you know, three weeks away from the month the Lord circled, and it was in red, and there was a cloud of dust on it.

00:03:00.443 --> 00:03:14.514
And He said, "This is a time of great change, great acceleration."And I thought, well, the Feast of Trumpets is in September, and that is the 23rd of September of this year.

00:03:14.515 --> 00:03:18.555
And so, could we have an event there that they sacrificed secretly?

00:03:18.556 --> 00:03:34.798
That, yeah, the heifers that they're telling you all about is in the front, and everybody said, "But they have one that's hidden in the back that they're not talking about just for safety."Because they said that if people knew where it was, people could try to hurt this thing.

00:03:34.799 --> 00:03:46.370
And if they hurt it and they do something to it or mess it up or whatever, it makes it not holy or sacrificable to be burnt or whatever they're going to do with it to make these ashes to build the third temple.

00:03:46.371 --> 00:03:53.651
It disqualifies it. So if they scar it, if they mess it up, you know, it disqualifies this red heifer so that they can't even use it.

00:03:53.652 --> 00:03:56.075
Yeah. Because it has to be without blemish. Without blemish.

00:03:56.076 --> 00:04:00.957
So they have to hide it. This red heifer is like cream of the crop.

00:04:00.958 --> 00:04:04.100
It's the best of the best, and it's probably worth a lot of money.

00:04:04.101 --> 00:04:10.320
So you hide it in an undisclosed location is what I believe, you know, and so let's just see what happens.

00:04:10.321 --> 00:04:23.926
If they come out on the 24th and say, "All right, we had our ceremony,"and they have pictures and they tell everybody and they get the ashes of it and they do everything, and they want to dedicate the temple and get ready for everything, I just think we're just right there.

00:04:23.927 --> 00:04:31.032
Could it be delayed? I don't see it. But, you know, I mean, anything's possible.

00:04:31.033 --> 00:04:46.086
But I'm just thinking, wow, Lord, could we have a distraction over here while doing something over here in the night where everybody's watching, "Oh no, bummer,"and all the Arab nations, everybody's like, "Well, we knew it was too good to be true, but you know, they all just leave it alone"?

00:04:46.087 --> 00:04:57.828
And then all of a sudden, they come out and go the day of, the day of or whatever, and have a big ceremony and tell everybody because they didn't want any kind of weirdness.

00:04:57.829 --> 00:05:03.778
So, we'll see. But we see Bibi saying we're going to take over Gaza. They want to do all this stuff.

00:05:03.779 --> 00:05:12.877
We see the meeting, another thing with President Trump and Putin in Alaska on the 15th.

00:05:12.878 --> 00:05:21.203
And this is what I thought was interesting, that Zelensky is saying, "We don't want nothing to do with it,"you know?

00:05:21.204 --> 00:05:25.913
Here Trump is trying to cause a peace thing and we're going to do this.

00:05:25.914 --> 00:05:34.837
We're going to talk. We just want to talk things through. And then we have the puppet Zelensky going over. Huh? Zelensky. Zelensky.

00:05:34.837 --> 00:05:40.739
We have the puppet over here doing exactly what I told you, Emmanuel Macron and all these, that they don't want peace.

00:05:40.740 --> 00:05:45.038
I've already warned you all. How many times did the spirit of the Lord—the Lord said, "You didn't warn them"?

00:05:45.039 --> 00:05:52.638
He did. When we were praying and the Lord said they don't want peace. They want to escalate this thing. Why?

00:05:52.639 --> 00:06:04.528
Because of financial things, oil agreements, major escalation of war to support the euro, to support their economies. And this was concerning Canada.

00:06:04.529 --> 00:06:23.230
And the Lord even showed me Mark and him over there, and he was talking to the weasel, and they were all, you know, with Europe and with—I'm sorry, with England and with all the other things going on with all these other nations, with Germany in the background trying to figure out how they could escalate.

00:06:23.231 --> 00:06:33.809
And that's what the Lord was so upset about this because He was saying, "What would it be if it was their sons and daughters on the frontline?"If you all remember that prayer time we had.

00:06:33.810 --> 00:06:41.338
So Trump, I told you, he said, "I want peace."He was in the midst of it saying, "We want prosperity.

00:06:41.339 --> 00:06:53.198
We want a golden age, a new crypto age. We want all this stuff."And he's in the background saying, "We could make America great again. We can make the world—let's have a trading thing.

00:06:53.199 --> 00:07:24.913
Let's—in my term, I want it to be one of the greatest comebacks of all time of the dollar, about money, about everything."And I told you all, when I saw the new digital age, it was a new industrial revolution that the Lord was showing us was going to take place, that He said, "Watch AI and what they do with AI."And even in not the last video, but the video before, the Lord kept talking about even with the healings and all this.

00:07:24.914 --> 00:07:30.828
And boy, there are some of you who got really upset about that. I'm not talking about AI being your healer.

00:07:30.829 --> 00:07:36.423
Jesus Christ, ladies and gentlemen, let me tell you this: Jesus Christ is the only healer.

00:07:36.424 --> 00:07:45.459
He paid the price of 39 stripes on His back so that every single one of you can walk in freedom from sickness and disease, any kind of, all of it.

00:07:45.460 --> 00:07:55.732
Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory over sickness. But can God use medical science to help you? Yes.

00:07:55.733 --> 00:08:11.867
And that's why I was trying to say—I even, even Oral Roberts raised up how many doctors through ORU to take to missionaries and help them to help these people that are sick, that modern science can help.

00:08:11.868 --> 00:08:16.398
I believe God is a good God and He can use anything He wants to use to help His people.

00:08:16.399 --> 00:08:33.408
He's not limited to say, "Well, you know, Jesus, I know He died for them, but if it comes down to modern science and it can help them, the only way through it is just by divine healing."I believe any kind of healing is divine healing.

00:08:33.409 --> 00:08:42.291
I believe anything that's good that comes from God is a healing, burden-removing, yoke-destroying power of God.

00:08:42.292 --> 00:08:54.432
That's like saying that somebody who's strung out on drugs can't go to rehab and get help, or if they have marriage problems, they can't get freedom and go to marriage counseling and talk it over.

00:08:54.433 --> 00:09:03.729
Well, you know, you go, and anything that's good that makes it better is good and it comes from God: counseling, therapy, whatever.

00:09:03.730 --> 00:09:10.919
The devil comes—and I'll say this again over and over and over again—the devil comes to kill, steal, and destroy.

00:09:10.920 --> 00:09:13.952
But God comes that we might have life, and life more abundantly.

00:09:13.953 --> 00:09:22.025
And whatever it takes you to get abundant life is God. Now, what's His perfect plan?

00:09:22.026 --> 00:09:28.994
Us to walk in divine health through His word. Yes. Do you hear that?

00:09:28.995 --> 00:09:42.473
His perfect plan is to walk in divine health through His word, finding scriptures that pertain to what you're believing for and standing on the word of God for the manifestation of what you're needing.

00:09:42.474 --> 00:09:49.026
Now, everybody's faith is at a different level. I have babies on here, and I have veterans on here.

00:09:49.027 --> 00:09:54.429
So, the veterans go, 'Hey, it should only be by the word of God.'But the babies are going, 'I don't know about the word of God.

00:09:54.430 --> 00:09:57.951
I just got born again yesterday, but I'm dying of this and I need help.

00:09:57.952 --> 00:10:07.700
But I found out if I go to the doctor, they'll help me.'Well, am I up in here to try to condemn you and say you shouldn't go get help? Heavens, no!

00:10:07.701 --> 00:10:22.728
It's like that—remember that joke where they said the guy was stranded on top of his house during a flood, and then a boat came by and he said, 'Hey brother, I see you're stranded there.

00:10:22.729 --> 00:10:43.859
Can I help you?'And he said, 'No.'He kept praying and saying, 'Lord, save me, help me.'And he said, 'No, I'm waiting on God to help me.'And then somebody else came by, like a helicopter or something, and tried to throw a lifeline down and help him, and he said, 'No, I'm waiting on God.'And then, sure enough, finally the flood rose high enough that he died.

00:10:43.860 --> 00:10:47.634
And then he went to heaven. And when he got there, he said, 'What happened?

00:10:47.635 --> 00:10:55.777
I prayed, and I used my faith, and I believed God that You would save me, but You never did.'And God said, 'I tried to.

00:10:55.778 --> 00:11:03.975
I sent the lifeboat. I sent the rescue helicopter. I sent all those people along your path, and you just didn't accept the help.'Right.

00:11:03.976 --> 00:11:10.319
And there are so many in the body of Christ who do exactly that. They only want divine encounters.

00:11:10.320 --> 00:11:15.166
And we have family that are like that, and I understand where you're faced.

00:11:15.167 --> 00:11:17.538
They say, 'Well, I don't even take a Tylenol if I have a headache.

00:11:17.539 --> 00:11:32.909
I don't do any of this stuff because I feel like it's going against the word of God.'But I'm like, I have family—even my grandpa wouldn't even go and put lotion on his hands because he thought it was against the word, because of using anything modern to heal him if it wasn't God healing him.

00:11:32.910 --> 00:11:39.532
And his hands would crack and bleed all winter long because he thought it was against the Bible to put lotion on his hands.

00:11:39.533 --> 00:11:53.873
I'm talking about spiritual bondage, to the point where my aunt got bit by a brown recluse as a young girl, and the authorities had to come and get my aunt from my grandparents to take her to the hospital.

00:11:53.874 --> 00:12:07.917
But by the time they took her and got her there, the brown recluse bite made her so sick that she became mentally handicapped and still is today, and still has massive seizures.

00:12:07.918 --> 00:12:14.418
And my grandfather's gone home to be with the Lord. But that was just the way it was.

00:12:14.419 --> 00:12:24.591
They just felt like anything that had to do with modern science, if it wasn't God touching you directly, then it wasn't God at all; you're just going to die.

00:12:24.592 --> 00:12:37.609
You know what I'm saying? And so my aunt is still mentally handicapped today, right now, and still has repercussions from that decision.

00:12:37.610 --> 00:12:42.872
And it was the wrong decision. It was the wrong—I'll say it right now—it was a wrong decision.

00:12:42.873 --> 00:12:49.039
She suffered her whole life because of someone else's decision, and it was because of that brown recluse.

00:12:49.040 --> 00:12:53.169
Now, that may make some people really mad, but I'm telling you, that's how extreme people get with this.

00:12:53.170 --> 00:13:02.165
I've been on the wrong side of this and the right side of it, watching people, and I'm telling you, there gets to be some bondage coming up in here where people can't even live.

00:13:02.166 --> 00:13:07.492
They go, 'Well, I can't even...'and you're like, 'There's a cure there.'I can tell you another one.

00:13:07.493 --> 00:13:18.239
There was another girl in that church who had problems, and they wouldn't even get her help, and DHS had to come and get her because the people were just being flaky.

00:13:18.240 --> 00:13:33.892
Yeah, you can get to the point where you're so religious and so brainwashed by things that it's like whenever they deal with snakes and dance around, you know, 'I'll touch any deadly thing and it won't harm me,'and they're dancing around with cobras and vipers and everything, and they bite them and they think, 'Well, I guess it wasn't meant for me to live.

00:13:33.893 --> 00:13:41.271
I must have had sin in my life because this cobra bit me, or the snake, or the copperhead, or whatever bit me, and I didn't go to the doctor to get it taken care of, so I died.

00:13:41.272 --> 00:13:45.296
But if it's meant for me to take up these serpents,'I'm telling people, there is life there.

00:13:45.297 --> 00:13:50.874
Those kind of people are out there. So, you just have to use wisdom in these last days is what I'm trying to say.

00:13:50.875 --> 00:13:54.773
I'm not trying to condemn anybody that doesn't believe in modern science.

00:13:54.774 --> 00:14:00.735
I'm not trying to say either way. I understand you follow the Holy Ghost for your life and don't be flaky.

00:14:00.736 --> 00:14:09.169
If you have a peace, you go with your peace, but there comes a point—there's wisdom behind everything we do.

00:14:09.170 --> 00:14:20.435
And God is a God of wisdom. And you say, 'Well, Brandon, I believe this.'I'm not trying to tell you to believe either way. I'm trying to tell you there's a balance of things.

00:14:20.436 --> 00:14:35.617
And I've seen both sides, and people get—when Megan was first diagnosed with autism, I was so scared because of the Word of Faith, of everybody saying you have what you say.

00:14:35.618 --> 00:14:41.752
Don't say that, because life and death is in the power of your tongue. Do you want that?

00:14:41.753 --> 00:15:00.072
And whenever I saw that she wasn't talking, I saw that things were going on with her and it was so bad, but I wouldn't allow other people to say the word 'autism.'In fact, if you said that word, I'd be ready to fight because I was scared of it.

00:15:00.073 --> 00:15:07.169
I was scared of the diagnosis of autism to the point where it was bondage.

00:15:07.170 --> 00:15:28.958
And even around her, we called it 'the A-word.'You know, 'the A-word, it looks like she might be...'It's flakiness, but that's where you get so much that you think, 'Well, I know that life and death is in the power of the tongue,'and I understand that you have what you say, you speak to the mountain, and you tell it to be removed and be cast into the sea, and if you don't doubt in your heart, you shall have whatsoever things you say.

00:15:28.959 --> 00:15:34.726
I believe that you are snared by the words of your mouth. I understand that.

00:15:34.727 --> 00:15:39.776
But there gets to be a point in time where you get flaky with stuff.

00:15:39.777 --> 00:15:46.274
And I'm not denying autism. I'm denying its right to be there.

00:15:46.274 --> 00:15:50.982
Yes, I'm denying its right to be there. I say it doesn't have a right to stay.

00:15:50.983 --> 00:16:08.228
I'm not denying the poor report of what all these neuropsychologists have said, because they're just doing their job, and all the therapists, and everybody who's ever tried to help us. At the beginning, we didn't want to do anything.

00:16:08.229 --> 00:16:19.707
But then the more we went to these therapists and the more they started helping us, you go, 'Well, is this God?'I was so grieved—I'm telling you all, this is a major deal because this is bondage.

00:16:19.708 --> 00:16:34.179
And I cried myself to sleep because of the diagnosis when the state people came into our house, and they evaluated her and they helped us, and they said, 'This is what she's going—what's the level that she's at,'and all the things.

00:16:34.180 --> 00:17:07.456
And when we went to the neuropsychologist, and the neuropsychologist told us, 'She'll be at this level for the rest of her life,'and all this death sentence is what you hear about a dream of what you had for your daughter, a marriage, a family, a job, everything that you ever wanted for her as a mom and a dad, to think that maybe one day, that moment of what that doctor was saying was basically a death sentence to those dreams.

00:17:07.457 --> 00:17:20.632
And at that time, that's all we could see. And in the midst, when you're that close to the trees and you can't see around them, and you have family telling you, 'Well, you know, it could be a devil.

00:17:20.633 --> 00:17:31.985
You know, if you just have faith, brother, and you go out there and pray and do this, and you fast more—you must not have enough faith to get her healed.'Do you know how that's like a kick in the gut?

00:17:31.986 --> 00:17:39.352
Especially from people that you love, and they tell you that kind of stuff, and they're so righteous and they can believe God for it so much better than you.

00:17:39.353 --> 00:17:42.114
But then you look at their life and they're more broken than you are.

00:17:42.115 --> 00:17:47.552
But they can't see outside of the trees because they're too close to their forest.

00:17:47.553 --> 00:17:52.959
They're broken. Their children are strung out on stuff. And you look at them and go, 'Come on, man.

00:17:52.960 --> 00:18:03.047
Everybody's a work in progress.'I'll tell you how many times I had people say, 'Well, you must have been in sin. You must be living in sin.

00:18:03.048 --> 00:18:10.692
What kind of sin do you have hidden in your closet that God's punishing you, and that all this happened?'And you know how many times I'd go home and just cry myself to sleep.

00:18:10.693 --> 00:18:14.255
I didn't know what kind of sin. I'd go and search all the time, 'Lord, what am I doing wrong?

00:18:14.256 --> 00:18:20.967
I must have a door open because the devil's up here eating my lunch and I don't know what to do,'and cry.

00:18:20.968 --> 00:18:25.976
That cost us our marriage. How many times did we say, 'I can't live this anymore.

00:18:25.977 --> 00:18:33.470
I have so much pressure on me. I've messed up time and time again,'blaming me, blaming Diana.

00:18:33.471 --> 00:18:43.740
'Whose fault is this?'And all it came down to is: God is a good God, and the devil is a bad devil. And what the devil meant for bad, God had to turn it for good.

00:18:43.741 --> 00:18:54.068
When I told you I had the visitation with the Lord, and He took me out of my body again—I jumped through that portal, you can go watch that video—He took me to the past.

00:18:54.069 --> 00:19:00.990
He said, 'I want to show you the power of a decision.'It was a beautiful visitation I had with the Lord.

00:19:00.991 --> 00:19:13.119
And He said, 'Whatever you do and you mess up on, Brandon, if you're upright with me and you're seeking me, you're not big enough to mess up your life.

00:19:13.120 --> 00:19:19.832
You're not big enough to mess up your life, Brandon. The footsteps of the righteous are ordered of the Lord.

00:19:19.832 --> 00:19:28.297
And no matter how bad you mess up, or if you think you've messed up and derailed your life, I can turn it on a dime, son.

00:19:28.298 --> 00:19:43.065
No matter how bad the shots did this, or how bad this was with Megan or whatever, I can turn it around if you just keep in faith and believe me for it.'There's nothing too big, and there's nothing too small.

00:19:43.066 --> 00:19:53.470
God has paid the price for it all. And I don't know why I got off on this today because that's not even where I was going, but somebody obviously needed to hear it.

00:19:53.471 --> 00:20:07.444
But I'm telling you, oh, I know why—where I was going was about the AI and the things that I've seen coming with the healings of diabetes, cancers, and all the things the Lord told me are coming.

00:20:07.445 --> 00:20:12.976
Like I told you all, if it was for Megan and they told me, 'Hey, we have a cure for autism tomorrow,'this guy right here...

00:20:12.977 --> 00:20:25.074
If they are not requiring a Mark of the Beast chip in my hand or something in my forehead, and if it's not working anti-Bible—if it goes against the Word of God, you don't do it.

00:20:25.075 --> 00:20:30.772
Right. If it goes against the Word of God, you say, 'No, no, and heck no!

00:20:30.773 --> 00:20:37.123
I'm not going down that road.'But if it's not, then what's wrong with you?

00:20:37.124 --> 00:20:40.988
I would say, 'Yes, I'm going. We're going to go tomorrow.'What is it?

00:20:40.989 --> 00:20:47.397
An IV or whatever pill, and she's fixed. She goes, 'Hi, Dad. How are you doing?'You can take it to the bank, I'm going to do it.

00:20:47.398 --> 00:20:52.228
Some vitamin that God made, that they just discovered helps it.

00:20:52.229 --> 00:20:56.968
Because I know there's things on this earth that He made for us.

00:20:56.969 --> 00:21:05.328
There's Scripture to even back it: herbs and plants for the service of man. He talks about that in the Bible in Genesis.

00:21:05.329 --> 00:21:15.151
He said, 'I have given you all the herbs, the dirt basically, the plants, and everything for the service of man, to the service of us.'Yes.

00:21:15.152 --> 00:21:25.778
So if He gave us herbs, plants, and things for vitamins to keep our bodies strong, especially with how depleted our soils are...

00:21:25.779 --> 00:21:32.256
I take vitamins. I take all kinds of supplements to keep healthy because what we eat is depleted.

00:21:32.257 --> 00:21:36.594
But I'm just trying to help you all because there's so many people who get in bondage to things.

00:21:36.595 --> 00:21:47.191
And you say, 'Well, you know, hey, if it's making you better and you're going from glory to glory...'If you're on drugs—I have so many people say, 'Brandon, I'm strung out.

00:21:47.192 --> 00:21:59.120
I do acid when I'm watching you. I do this, I do that'—well, God doesn't want you on acid, man. God doesn't want you on meth. God doesn't want you on crack.

00:21:59.121 --> 00:22:07.999
God doesn't want you smoking marijuana and trying to see over in the spirit—you're going to get snared by a devil.

00:22:08.000 --> 00:22:20.646
The only pure way you're going to see in the spirit is not by a hallucinogen like, 'I do acid and I want to see over.'No, that is demonic spirits trying to mess with you, okay?

00:22:20.647 --> 00:22:28.239
It's only by the anointing and by the glory of God. That's the only way you're going to see and hear the Holy Spirit for real.

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:37.126
So get sold out and get radical. Fast a little bit. Seek His face and you will find Him. Knock and the door will be opened unto you.

00:22:37.127 --> 00:22:42.660
Good measure, pressed down, shaken together, and running over as you give; men will give unto your bosom.

